06:44.020 --> 06:46.620
is that you cannot pay for God.

06:46.620 --> 06:49.520
You see it's a living process of a living God.

06:49.520 --> 06:51.600
Now supposing you want to sprout a seed.

06:51.600 --> 06:54.320
How much money do you pay to the Mother Earth?

06:54.330 --> 06:57.020
It's a very simple thing, but people don't understand.

06:57.020 --> 07:00.120
They think that they can purchase everything.

07:00.120 --> 07:02.320
You cannot purchase God.

07:02.320 --> 07:06.620
A simple method if you apply to all of them they will all run away.

07:06.740 --> 07:14.020
Yes, now again. I read that the Spirit, this power you speak of, can deal with ...common

