07:44.420 --> 07:48.920
means we become too emotional or do all kinds of wrong nonsensical conditionings,

07:49.120 --> 07:54.420
then or if you go too much to the right in ego and all that, you see, then we break.

07:54.420 --> 07:57.520
Once we break this what happens that

07:57.520 --> 08:03.020
